&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;teknology RADAR “C&amp;amp;SI for IoT Solutions in Europe 2018” – Digital Factory&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;figure&quot;&gt;
   &lt;div class=&quot;figure-img&quot;&gt;
