                    &lt;td class=&quot;col&quot;&gt;Pearson, LinkedIn, Boston Scientific, BMC Software, ADP, Baker Tilly, Comcast, NBC-Universal, Spotify, Western Union, Box, Cisco&lt;/td&gt;
                    &lt;/tr&gt;
                    &lt;tr class=&quot;row  justify-content-center&quot;&gt;
